item.title: No Love In This Timeline | Glitchtale Season 2
item.description: For once, nobody died! I applaud you Camila for holding back this one episode! Then again, it is only Part 1 so if Part 2 has deaths I guess someone did die, in that case, NotLikeThis Camila!
